Introspection utility for Ruby language.

Usage:
  <%= values[:program] %> [command] [options]
  <%= values[:program] %> help <command>
  <%= values[:program] %> --help
  <%= values[:program] %> --version

Commands:
<% values[:commands].sort_by { |name, description| name }.each do |name, description| -%>
  <%= "%-16s" % name %>  <%= description %>
<% end -%>

Options:
      --help        Show this help end exit.
      --version     Show application version end exit.
